itu1665703200746.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/itu1665703200746.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/itu1665703200746.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"itu1665703200746\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Set the repeat count for the UTIMER component.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"itu1665703200746__topic_d136142e1_d136143e1_d136144e1\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104itu1665703200746_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"itu1665703200746__codeblock_x4d_klg_hwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">operation setRepeat\n params\n      numeric Count : IN\n endparams</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"itu1665703200746__section_kk2_llg_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d891485e56\">Parameters</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"itu1665703200746__p_d136148e1_d136149e1_d136150e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Count</var>—integer that specifies how\n            many times the current instance of the UTIMER component will send its message.\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code> indicates unlimited repetition. The default is\n            <code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"itu1665703200746__section_pql_nlg_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d891485e73\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"itu1665703200746__p_d136070e1_d136071e1_d136072e1\">The value returned in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span> is\n            always <code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"itu1665703200746__section_ant_4lg_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d891485e88\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"itu1665703200746__p_d135212e1_d135213e1_d135214e1\">Allowed in all Uniface component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"itu1665703200746__section_kgz_plg_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d891485e97\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"itu1665703200746__p_d136166e1_d136167e1_d136168e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">setRepeat()</span> operation sets\n            the repeat count for the current instance of the UTIMER component.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528705\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528705\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "setRepeat() Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 25, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Set the repeat count for the UTIMER component. Explain this code operation setRepeat params numeric Count : IN endparams Copy Parameters Count —integer that specifies how many times the current instance of the UTIMER component will send its message. 0 indicates unlimited repetition. The default is 1 . Return Values The value returned in $status is always 0 . Use Allowed in all Uniface component types. Description The setRepeat() operation sets the repeat count for the current instance of the UTIMER component. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}